/>\n<br />\ncity多數圍威喂，啲fd通常都係hall/doc/ ocamp/ 你果科啲人<br />\ncu 圈子會大啲<br />\n<br />\ncity啲hall 十一棟聚埋一齊<br />\ncu跟書院<br />\n<br />\ncity 除左中英文3仔班(如果你3左) ， UE, cciv, 你果科既英文外( e.g. bba-》 business communication ) 要讀4 定唔知5個<br />\n elective (唔記得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n但以上都冇考試，得主科果啲有<br />\n中文 year1要 reg pe，其餘唔清楚 <br />\n諗到再講"},{"pid":"b0a2073907034f555ad364b6f51cdecaad6321f3","tid":215253,"uid":74687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T11:07:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>呢啲垃圾就唔好成日拎出黎講啦</blockquote><br />\nDse仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1t8t21f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1t8t21f.jpg&h=063c492b&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">屌 仲以為幾撚勁罵人垃圾 dse得果廿分 仲要英文得3 垃圾都輪唔到你到<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">讀</span></blockquote><br />\n但係shitty除咗bba真係垃圾喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n中大點都有仲medic law撐住，城大有排追<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">中大law<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同city law冇分別</span></blockquote><br />\n都仲有gbus喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1eaada283d28fa5a6c374078aa16664cfb691885","tid":215253,"uid":101341,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T11:07:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>利申先 shitty仔BBA<br />\n認真答:<br />\n其實個獸醫course好似未認可<br />\n<br />\n至於邊間好就睇你讀乜科同睇你鍾意邊種文化<br />\nQS排名 city啱啱過CU頭<br />\n而city近期排名都的確係升得快<br />\n但其實個排名冇乜用<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nbba有啲科cu好啲有啲科city好啲<br />\n例如gbus cu應該只排係ust後<br />\ncity就啱